items.title: In pictures: Eid celebrations around the world

items.title: Trump says he 'couldn't care less' about higher car prices

items.title: Why British boarding schools are so eager to open in Nigeria
items.description: With UK school fees rising, Nigeria's elite can now choose to give their offspring a British education at home.
